import React from 'react'
import Home from './component/services/Home'
import Technicians from './component/services/Technicians'
import Professional from './component/services/Professional'
import Consultation from './component/services/Consultation'
import Brands from './component/services/Brands'
import Updates from './component/services/Updates'


export default function s() {
  return (
    <>
      <Home />
      <Technicians />
      <Professional/>
      <Consultation/>
      <Brands/>
      <Updates/>
    </>
  )
}
